---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'How much does a 50-flat society cost each month?',
    answer: 'A 50-flat community costs ₹1,000/month on Dwell Hub. That includes the core society workflows committees usually need, such as billing, complaints, visitor tracking, reports, and resident self-service.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How secure is our society data?',
    answer: 'We utilize bank-grade 256-bit encryption and ISO-certified data centers. Your community data is siloed and protected by rigorous access control protocols.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can we import our existing flat data?',
    answer: 'Yes. Upload your flat inventory via Excel with flat numbers, types, and floor details. The system maps blocks, floors, and units automatically — most societies are fully set up within an hour.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can residents pay via credit cards?',
    answer: 'Yes, we support all major credit/debit cards, UPI, and net banking via PhonePe. Payments reconcile instantly and residents can track their payment history from their dashboard.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Does Dwell Hub work on mobile devices?',
    answer: 'Absolutely. Dwell Hub has a dedicated Android app available on the Google Play Store, and an iOS app is coming soon. You can also install it as a Progressive Web App on any device — just open app.dwellhub.in in your browser, tap Share or Menu, and select "Add to Home Screen" for a native app-like experience.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What reports can we generate for our AGM?',
    answer: 'Dwell Hub generates P&L statements, collection reports with payment-status breakdowns, defaulter lists with outstanding amounts per flat, and category-wise expense summaries. All reports are filterable by date range.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How are committee roles handled?',
    answer: 'The platform supports distinct roles for Secretary, Joint Secretary, Treasurer, and Admin — each with appropriate permissions. Committee members access only the tools relevant to their responsibilities.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Can we track visitors and deliveries at the gate?',
    answer: 'Yes. Dwell Hub includes Gate Management for recording visitor and delivery entries with flat mapping, key contact details, and role-based visibility. Security or service staff can log entries quickly, while admins can review entry activity across the society.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How do I get started with my society?',
    answer: 'Click "Get Started" and fill in your society details. After setup, you can add blocks, flats, and residents from the dashboard. The platform is designed for fast self-serve onboarding with support available by email when needed.',
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
    <div class="lg:col-span-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary tracking-tight mb-6 font-headline">Curated Answers</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body mb-8">Quick resolutions for common resident inquiries regarding our platform and services.</p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary mb-3 font-label">Support Desk</p>
          <a href="mailto:support@dwellhub.in" class="text-primary font-headline font-bold text-base break-all hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity">
            support@dwellhub.in
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body mt-2">
            Product help, onboarding questions, billing clarifications, and resident support.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-primary mb-3 font-label">Marketing Desk</p>
          <a href="mailto:marketing@dwellhub.in" class="text-primary font-headline font-bold text-base break-all hover:opacity-75 transition-opacity">
            marketing@dwellhub.in
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body mt-2">
            Partnerships, demos, campaigns, and society outreach requests.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((faq) => (
        <details class="group bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 open:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            <span>{faq.question}</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm font-body">
            {faq.answer}
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
